/**
 * Apex Design Patterns - 	Chapter 3
 * Author				-	Jitendra Zaa
 * Example of Decorator Pattern. Base abstract class to be used in composite pattern.
 * */
public abstract class SalesforceSupport {  
    
    public virtual String getDescription(){
        return 'This is base Abstract class';
    } 
    
    /**
     * This methods must be implemented by all child classes.
     * It returns total cost to resolve case of specified type.
     * */
    public abstract Double getCost();
    
}